document_notes.text:
This update for rubygem-activesupport-5_1 fixes the following issues:

- CVE-2020-8165: Fixed deserialization of untrusted data in MemCacheStore potentially resulting in remote code execution (bsc#1172186)

notes.text: A deserialization of untrusted data vulnernerability exists in rails < 5.2.4.3, rails < 6.0.3.1 that can allow an attacker to unmarshal user-provided objects in MemCacheStore and RedisCacheStore potentially resulting in an RCE.
